  <para xml:id="p11">
    <equation labels="LABEL:eq:E" xml:id="S0.E2">
      <tags>
        <tag>(2)</tag>
        <tag role="autoref">Equation 2</tag>
        <tag role="refnum">2</tag>
      </tags>
      <Math mode="display" tex="E(r,u)=\partial_{s^{\prime}}L(r,u^{-},u)+\partial_{s}L(r,u,u^{+})=\left\langle%&#10;\frac{\Delta r^{-}}{|\Delta r^{-}|}-\frac{\Delta r}{|\Delta r|},\dot{r}(u)%&#10;\right\rangle." text="E * open-interval@(r, u) = (partial-differential _ (s ^ prime))@(L) * vector@(r, u ^ -, u) + (partial-differential _ s)@(L) * vector@(r, u, u ^ +) = list@((Delta * r ^ -) / absolute-value@(Delta * r ^ -) - (Delta * r) / absolute-value@(Delta * r), dot@(r) * u)" xml:id="S0.E2.m1">
        <XMath>
          <XMDual>
            <XMRef idref="S0.E2.m1.10"/>
            <XMWrap>
              <XMApp xml:id="S0.E2.m1.10">
                <XMTok meaning="multirelation"/>
                <XMApp>
                  <XMTok meaning="times" role="MULOP">⁢</XMTok>
                  <XMTok font="italic" role="UNKNOWN">E</XMTok>
                  <XMDual>
                    <XMApp>
                      <XMTok meaning="open-interval"/>
                      <XMRef idref="S0.E2.m1.3"/>
                      <XMRef idref="S0.E2.m1.4"/>
                    </XMApp>
                    <XMWrap>
                      <XMTok role="OPEN" stretchy="false">(</XMTok>

    <equation xml:id="S0.Ex37">
      <Math mode="display" tex="\|\partial_{12}L(u,u^{+})\|_{\sigma}\leq C\frac{\|\dot{r}\|_{\sigma}^{2}}{\min%&#10;\|\Delta r\|}+C\frac{\|\Delta r\|_{\sigma}^{2}\|\dot{r}\|_{\sigma}^{2}}{\min\|%&#10;\Delta r\|^{3}}\leq C\alpha^{-1}." text="(norm@((partial-differential _ 12)@(L) * open-interval@(u, u ^ +))) _ sigma less= C * (((norm@(dot@(r))) _ sigma) ^ 2 / minimum@(norm@(Delta * r))) + C * ((((norm@(Delta * r)) _ sigma) ^ 2 * ((norm@(dot@(r))) _ sigma) ^ 2) / minimum@((norm@(Delta * r)) ^ 3)) less= C * alpha ^ (- 1)" xml:id="S0.Ex37.m1">
        <XMath>
          <XMDual>
            <XMRef idref="S0.Ex37.m1.7"/>
            <XMWrap>
              <XMApp xml:id="S0.Ex37.m1.7">
                <XMTok meaning="multirelation"/>
                <XMApp>

    <equation xml:id="S0.Ex54">
      <Math mode="display" tex="\|r_{+}-r\|_{\sigma^{\prime},2}&lt;\frac{D_{4}q\epsilon}{(\sigma-\sigma^{\prime})%&#10;^{2}},\quad\|v\|_{\sigma^{\prime}}&lt;D_{4}q\epsilon," text="formulae@((norm@(r _ + - r)) _ (list@(sigma ^ prime, 2)) less (D _ 4 * q * epsilon) / (sigma - sigma ^ prime) ^ 2, (norm@(v)) _ (sigma ^ prime) less D _ 4 * q * epsilon)" xml:id="S0.Ex54.m1">

    <equation xml:id="S0.Ex91">
      <Math mode="display" tex="\|r_{*}-r\|_{\sigma^{\prime},2}\leq\frac{C}{(\sigma-\sigma^{\prime})}\|a\|_{%&#10;\sigma,2}\leq\frac{Cq\epsilon}{(\sigma-\sigma^{\prime})}." text="(norm@(r _ * - r)) _ (list@(sigma ^ prime, 2)) less= (C / (sigma - sigma ^ prime)) * (norm@(a)) _ (list@(sigma, 2)) less= (C * q * epsilon) / (sigma - sigma ^ prime)" xml:id="S0.Ex91.m1">
        <XMath>
          <XMDual>
            <XMRef idref="S0.Ex91.m1.8"/>
            <XMWrap>
              <XMApp xml:id="S0.Ex91.m1.8">
